snippet.title: KHADPANCH | Episode 1 - P.O.V | Latest Punjabi Web Series 2025 | à¨–à©œà¨ªà©°à¨š All Episodes Available on YT
snippet.description:
In a small village plagued by a rising tide of drug-related deaths, the mysterious overdose of a young man named Babbu sparks a web of suspicion and intrigue.

After the success of "Yaar Jigree Kasooti Degree" and "Yaar Chale Bahar"  Troll Punjabi is back with a Mystery Series "KHADPANCH" - A gripping tale of a Punjab's Village torn apart by addiction, secrets, and the relentless pursuit of justice.


Edited, Produced, Written & Directed - Rabby Tiwana (Insta :-  @rabbytiwana)

Starring - Amrit Amby (IG : @amritamby),  Sukh Pindi Wala AKA Dhutta (IG : @pindi_ala),  Amrita Amme (IG : @Amrita Amme), Butta Badbar (IG : @buttabadbar).

Theme Song Credits
Vocals - Gurpreet Singh, Gron Sukhija
Music - Gurpreet Singh (Hertz Music Studio)
Lyrics - Kunwar Partap

Challi Jandi Ee Credits
Singer/Lyrics/Compose: Rythm Mansa
Music/Mix/Master: IGMOR
Link :  https://youtu.be/sLNbOkDLoSc

Co-Starring - Rhythempreet Kaur (IG:@iamrhythem), Sukhwinder Sohi (IG: @Sukhwindersohi26), Manoj Chaunda, Renu Sidak ( IG :renusidakofficial), Deepanshi Parvesh Bhanot ( IG: @deepanshi_parvesh), Karishma Rattan (IG : @ikarishmarattan) , Babar (IG : @actorbabar1),Rang Harjinder (IG :@rangharjinder), Sukhjit Sharma (IG :@sukhjitsharma), Amrit Dhalio (IG: @Amrit_dhaliozz), Arry Singh Gill (IG: @Arrygillofficial), Baljit Singh Balli (IG: @baljitballi001), Gagandeep Singh (@gagan.sandhuz), Jasveer Kaur Jassi, Jasmeen Meenu (IG: @jasmeen_mennu), Sunny Sunam (IG: @sunny43727), Harman, Pardeep Singh,  Preet Karkhal, Manveer Ramgharia, Kiranpaal Gaga, Jagtar Benipal, Pinky Sagoo, Harvinder Dhindsa,Hardeep Dhindsa, Shaminder Kaur chahal, Charanjeet singh, Vicky Bhardwaj, Gagan Kalyan, Karamjit Kaur, Toni Khatra, Anju Saini.

Crew Of Kharpanch : 

Cinematographer - Sukhan Saar
Chief AD - Angad Sadana
Executive Producer - Amrinder Singh Sidhu (Laddi Pakhon)
Art Director -  Parminder Singh (Laddi  Sangtiwala)
Production Head - Robin Robbie
Line Producer - Karanveer Brar
Co - Writers - Naseem Bajwa & Jass Dhillon

Featuring Veer Pahariya and Sara Ali Khan, with lyrics by Irshad Kamil and music by Tanishk Bagchi, this song will surely strike a chord in your heart.

Chan chan ke

Tu ishq hai toh main baahon mein hoon
Baahon mein hoon toh panaahon mein hoon
Kajal hoon toh main nigahon mein hoon
Tu hain toh main hoon

Kasme vaade kyun tu hain toh main hoon

Seene pe likh loon tu hain toh main hoon
Tu hain toh main hoon

Zindagi bhar chup rahoonga baatein dil ki bol ke

Main sadke main tere apni khushi de doonga tol ke

Main koi tera hi armaan hoon
Tu hain toh main hoon

Jhoothe Judaiyan
Jhoothe  bichhode

Yaad kahe yeh humse aksar
Tu hain toh main hoon

snippet.title: Snow Day Vlog in Tamil | Making a Snow Man | Steffi Ulagam
snippet.description:
In this video join me during our recent experience with snow fall. We had never experienced this heavy snow before and we had a great time playing with snow balls and we also built a snowman. Alandra had a great time playing in the snow. We had already protected the cold sensitive plants in the greenhouse and wrapped others. It was a very good experience having snow as a temporary guest and seeing the whole landscape in a bright white color. 

Friends, hope you like today's vlog. See you soon with more interesting vlogs.

snippet.title: HIGHLIGHTS | PSG 4-2 MAN CITY | Grealish, Haaland Goals | UEFA Champions League
snippet.description:
City will need to beat Club Brugge next week to qualify for the Champions League play-off round after a 4-2 defeat to PSG.
The Blues saw a two -goal lead slip against the impressive French champions who responded with an outstanding fight-back

After a goalless first-half, quickfire second period goals from Jack Grealish and Erling Haaland looked to have set City on the road to a priceless victory.

But two goals in four minutes for PSG wiped out our advantage in the blink of an eye, a third from Joao Neves 12 minutes from time and a GonÃ§alo Ramos fourth with the last kick of the game gave the Ligue 1 champions a dramatic 4-2 win.

snippet.title: Mickey 17 | Official Trailer 2
snippet.description:
Heâ€™s dying to save mankind. #Mickey17 â€“ only in theaters March 7.

From the Academy Award-winning writer/director of â€œParasite,â€ Bong Joon Ho, comes his next groundbreaking cinematic experience, â€œMickey 17.â€ The unlikely hero, Mickey Barnes (Robert Pattinson) has found himself in the extraordinary circumstance of working for an employer who demands the ultimate commitment to the jobâ€¦ to die, for a living.

Written and directed by Bong Joon Ho, â€œMickey 17â€ stars Robert Pattinson (â€œThe Batman,â€ â€œTenetâ€), Naomi Ackie (â€œStar Wars: Episode IX â€“ The Rise of Skywalkerâ€), Academy Award nominee Steven Yeun (â€œMinari,â€ â€œBeefâ€), with Academy Award nominee Toni Collette (â€œHereditaryâ€), and Academy Award nominee Mark Ruffalo (â€œPoor Thingsâ€). 

The film is produced by Dede Gardner and Jeremy Kleiner (Oscar winners for â€œMoonlightâ€ and â€œ12 Years a Slaveâ€), Bong Joon Ho and Dooho Choi (â€œOkja,â€ â€œSnowpiercerâ€). It is based on the novel Mickey 7 by Edward Ashton. The executive producers are Brad Pitt, Jesse Ehrman, Peter Dodd and Marianne Jenkins. The director of photography is Darius Khondji (Oscar nomination for â€œBardo: False Chronicle of a Handful of Truths,â€ â€œOkjaâ€). The production designer is Fiona Crombie (Oscar nomination for â€œThe Favourite,â€ â€œCruellaâ€). It is edited by Yang Jinmo (Oscar nomination for â€œParasite,â€ â€œOkjaâ€). The music is by Jung Jaeil (â€œParasite,â€ â€œSquid Gameâ€). The visual effects supervisor is Dan Glass (â€œFantastic Beasts: The Secrets of Dumbledore,â€ â€œFast & Furious Presents: Hobbs & Shawâ€). The costume designer is Catherine George (â€œOkja,â€ Snowpiercerâ€). 

Warner Bros. Pictures presents A Plan B Entertainment Production, An Offscreen Production / A Kate Street Picture Company Production, A Film By Bong Joon Ho: â€œMickey 17.â€ The film will be distributed worldwide by Warner Bros. Pictures, in theaters only nationwide on March 7, 2025, and internationally beginning on 5 March 2025.

About Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah: 
----------------------------------------------------------------------
The show is inspired by the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chasma' by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr Tarak Mehta. This story evolves around happenings in "Gokuldham Co-operative Society" and covers topical issues that are socially relevant. The show predominantly revolves around 'Jethalaal' (Dilip Joshi), an uneducated Gujarati businessman. Your 'Taarak Mehta' (Sailesh Lodha), is his neighbour. 'Jethalaal' finds a friend and philosopher in 'Taarak Mehta' and often goes to him for advice whenever he is in trouble. Jethalaal's family includes his simpleton wife 'Daya Ben' (Disha Wakani) and a mischievous son 'Tapu' (Raj Anankat). Tapu is a menace and a constant source of trouble to all the members of Gokuldham. They have often warned 'Jethalaal' to reform 'Tapu' or be prepared to leave the premises.
